der-menu-button-icon\"><span class=\"header-menu-button-icon__bar header-menu-button-icon__bar--top\"></span><span class=\"header-menu-button-icon__bar header-menu-button-icon__bar--bottom\"></span></span><span class=\"header-menu-button-state\">メニュー</span></button>\n    <nav class=\"header-menu\" id=\"header-menu\">\n      <ul class=\"header-nav\">\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/number\">数字で見るICS</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/message\">社長メッセージ</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/work\">仕事を知る</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/people\">人を知る</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/place\">職場を知る</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/info\">募集要項</a></li>\n      </ul>\n      <p class=\"recruit-header-recruit\"> <a class=\"recruit-header-recruit-button\" href=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/27/pc/search/corp63373/outline.html\" target=\"_blank\"> <span class=\"recruit-header-recruit-button__text\">ENTRY</span></a></p>\n    </nav>\n  </header><main class=\"recruit-main\">\n\t<div class=\"recruit-page-header\">\n\t\t<div class=\"container\">\n\t\t\t<h1 class=\"recruit-page-title\" data-english=\"PLACE\"><span class=\"recruit-page-title__text\">職場を知る</span></h1>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"recruit-page-body\">\n\t\t\n<div class=\"recruit-place-anchor-link\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<ul class=\"row row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-4 g-3 list-unstyled mb-0\">\n<li class=\"col\"><a class=\"recruit-anchor-link-button\" href=\"#recruit-work-environment\"> <span class=\"recruit-anchor-link-button__text\">働く環境</span><span class=\"recruit-anchor-link-button__angle\"></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"col\"><a class=\"recruit-anchor-link-button\" href=\"#recruit-work-training\"> <span class=\"recruit-anchor-link-button__text\">社員研修</span><span class=\"recruit-anchor-link-button__angle\"></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"col\"><a class=\"recruit-anchor-link-button\" href=\"#recruit-work-welfare\"> <span class=\"recruit-anchor-link-button__text\">福利厚生</span><span class=\"recruit-anchor-link-button__angle\"></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"col\"><a class=\"recruit-anchor-link-button\" href=\"#recruit-work-circle\"> <span class=\"recruit-anchor-link-button__text\">サークル活動</span><span class=\"recruit-anchor-link-button__angle\"></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<section class=\"recruit-page-bg recruit-page-bg--gradient mt-0 pt-0\" id=\"recruit-work-environment\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<h2 class=\"recruit-protrusion-heading\">働く環境</h2>\n<ul class=\"row row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3 g-3 list-unstyled mb-0\">\n<li class=\"col\"><span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle\"><span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-text\"><span class=\"d-block\"> <span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-underline\"><span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-text-large\">地元に根付いた</span></span></span><span class=\"d-block\"> <span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-underline\"><span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-text-large\">ライフスタイル</span></span>が</span>実現できます</span></span></li>\n<li class=\"col\"><span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle\"><span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-text\"><span class=\"d-block\"> <span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-underline\"><span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-text-large\">数十種類</span>以上</span>を超える</span><span class=\"d-block\"> 豊富な<span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-underline\"><span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-text-large\">研修制度</span></span>で</span><span class=\"d-block\">キャリアに応じた</span><span class=\"d-block\"> <span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-underline\"><span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-text-large\">スキルアップ</span></span>が</span>可能です</span></span></li>\n<li class=\"col\"><span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle\"><span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-text\"><span class=\"d-block\"> <span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-underline\"><span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-text-large\">プログラミング未経験</span></span></span><span class=\"d-block\">でも時間をかけて</span><span class=\"d-block\"> <span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-underline\"> <span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-text-large\">社員</span></span>を<span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-underline\"> <span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-text-large\">じっくり</span></span>、</span><span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-underline\"> <span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-text-large\">大切</span></span>に<span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-underline\"> <span class=\"recruit-work-place-circle-text-large\">成長させます</span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"d-block maw-780 mx-auto mt-60\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"border-radius-20 d-block mx-auto\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-1.jpg\" srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-1@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\">\n<figcaption class=\"image-caption before-triangle-up\">盛岡本社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"recruit-page-bg recruit-page-bg--white mt-0 pt-0\" id=\"recruit-work-training\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<h2 class=\"recruit-protrusion-heading\">社員研修</h2>\n<h3 class=\"heading-underline\">育成の全体像</h3>\n<p>社内研修と社内の育成制度により技術力の向上と業務知識の豊富な技術者の育成を目指します。</p>\n<p class=\"text-center mt-3 mb-0\"><picture> <source srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-2-pc.png 1x, /ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-2-pc@2x.png 2x\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-2-sp.png\" srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-2-sp@2x.png 2x\" alt=\"育成の全体像の図\"> </picture></p>\n<h3 class=\"heading-underline mt-100\">入社１年目研修は新入社員研修だけではありません</h3>\n<p>入社１年目は入社前の「新入社員導入研修」と併せて４講座を実施します。<br>入社時の新入社員研修は、社内講師の講座、社外講師のビジネスマナー講座の他に技術研修を約２ケ月間受講します。また、入社半年後には、フォロー研修、ビジネス対応術に関する研修の２講座を受講します。半年間、実務を経験した上で改めて研修を受講することにより、研修内容が身近に感じられ実務に取り入れやすく成長に繋がります。</p>\n<h4 class=\"heading-color before-triangle mt-40\">入社1年目社員研修</h4>\n<p class=\"text-center mt-3 mb-0\"><picture> <source srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-3-pc.png 1x, /ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-3-pc@2x.png 2x\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-3-sp.png\" srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-3-sp@2x.png 2x\" alt=\"入社前:新人社員導入研修、入社〜3ヶ月後:新人社員研修、6ヶ月後:入社1年目フォロー研修、その後:顧客満足を生み出すビジネス対応術（初級編）\"> </picture></p>\n<h3 class=\"heading-underline mt-100\">入社後5年目まで年度別研修があります</h3>\n<p>入社１年目～入社５年目までは、毎年必ず研修を受講します。<br>入社１年目から毎年ステップアップした研修内容で 入社５年目にはその集大成として「技術論文発表会」を実施しています。技術論文を作成することは勿論、各自プレゼン用の資料も作成し社員の前で発表を行います。発表内容は、各自が担った業務の成果発表、今後より良いシステムを提供するための提案等様々です。技術論文発表を経験することにより技術の研鑽にも繋がっています。</p>\n<h4 class=\"heading-color before-triangle mt-40\">入社年度別研修</h4>\n<p class=\"text-center mt-3 mb-0\"><picture> <source srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-4-pc.png 1x, /ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-4-pc@2x.png 2x\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-4-sp.png\" srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-4-sp@2x.png 2x\" alt=\"入社1年目:ピジネスマナーの基本を習得する、初級SEとしての基礎を習得する、問題解決・改善しようとする意識を高める（対象講座:新入社員研修、入社1年目「フォロー研修」、顧客満足を生出すビジネス対応術研修（初級編））、入社2年目:自分の立場と組織の役割を確認し、自分の将来像を考える。自己表現力を高める（対象講座:入社2年目「スキルアップ研修」）、入社3年目:中堅社員としての自覚を持つ。論理的に考えるスキル、口頭表現のスキル、文章表現のスキル向上を図る（対象講座:CSマインド研修（基本編）、入社3年目「IT技術者のためのコミュニケーション」）、入社4・5年目:技術論文の書き方を通じて、業務に関する研究心を養成する。公式の場で発表することで、プレゼンテーション能力を身に付ける（対象講座:論文の書き方、プレゼンテーション、技術論文発表会）\"> </picture></p>\n<h3 class=\"heading-underline mt-100\">入社後5年目以降の社内研修</h3>\n<div class=\"row gy-5 gy-lg-0\">\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"d-block mx-auto\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-5.png\" srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-5@2x.png 2x\" alt=\"ICS人材の育成の図\">\n<h4 class=\"heading-color text-center mt-30\">技術面だけでなく多面的な人材育成</h4>\n<p class=\"text-center mb-0\"><span class=\"d-md-block\">新入社員研修から入社年度別研修を終えた後は</span>引き続き技術力とヒューマンスキルの向上を目指します。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"d-block mx-auto\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-6.png\" srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-6@2x.png 2x\" alt=\"段階的・継続的な人材育成の図\">\n<h4 class=\"heading-color text-center mt-30\">段階的・継続的な人材育成</h4>\n<p class=\"text-center mb-0\"><span class=\"d-md-block\">入社時から継続的な学びを継続することで、</span><span class=\"d-md-block\">技術力だけでなく複合的な知識を身に付けます。</span>最終的には技術や業務のスペシャリストを目指します。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"heading-underline mt-100\">各種の充実した研修制度　スペシャリスト用研修も開催</h3>\n<h4 class=\"heading-color before-square text-danger\">年度別研修　役職別研修</h4>\n<p>社員研修は、様々なテーマで入社年度や資格等級に合わせて実施しています。各役職に昇格した際には、必ず研修を受講します。その他各テーマにおいても研修を実施していますので、必要に応じて受講します。</p>\n<h4 class=\"heading-color before-square text-danger mt-40\">一般研修　技術研修　 スペシャリスト研修</h4>\n<p>全社員対象の一般研修のほかに、全社員の8割を占める技術職社員対象の技術研修が用意されています。自社内での技術研修はもちろん社外研修への参加も活発で各種団体・メーカ・専門機関などでの場も用意されます。さらに高度資格保持者などスペシャリスト向けの研修も開講しています。</p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"recruit-page-bg recruit-page-bg--gray mt-0 pt-0\" id=\"recruit-work-welfare\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<h2 class=\"recruit-protrusion-heading\">福利厚生</h2>\n<h3 class=\"heading-underline\">充実した福利厚生で社員の健康や生活をサポート</h3>\n<div class=\"row g-3\">\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n<div class=\"white-panel h-100\">\n<h4 class=\"heading-color heading-color--large text-center\">社会保険</h4>\n<ul class=\"row row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-2 g-3 list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"col\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">健康保険</span></li>\n<li class=\"col\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">厚生年金</span></li>\n<li class=\"col\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">確定給付年金</span></li>\n<li class=\"col\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">雇用保険</span></li>\n<li class=\"col\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">労災保険</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n<div class=\"white-panel h-100\">\n<h4 class=\"heading-color heading-color--large text-center\">休暇制度</h4>\n<ul class=\"row row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-2 g-3 list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"col\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">年次有給休暇</span></li>\n<li class=\"col\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">年末年始休暇</span></li>\n<li class=\"col\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">夏季休暇</span></li>\n<li class=\"col\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">誕生日休暇</span></li>\n<li class=\"col\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">結婚記念日休暇</span></li>\n<li class=\"col\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">出産育児休暇制度</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"text-primary fw-bold text-end\">等々</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col\">\n<div class=\"white-panel\">\n<h4 class=\"heading-color heading-color--large text-center\">その他</h4>\n<ul class=\"row g-3 list-unstyled\">\n<li class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">社員持株会</span></li>\n<li class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">財形制度</span></li>\n<li class=\"col-lg-6\"><span class=\"welfare-item\"> <span class=\"d-block d-md-inline\">確定拠出年金制度</span>（従業員拠出制度あり）</span></li>\n<li class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">各種保養所</span></li>\n<li class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">宿泊補助制度</span></li>\n<li class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">提携スキー場利用</span></li>\n<li class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">住宅購入割引制度</span></li>\n<li class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">住宅金利優遇制度</span></li>\n<li class=\"col-lg-4\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">各種保険団体扱い対象</span></li>\n<li class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">海外研修制度</span></li>\n<li class=\"col-lg-2\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">互助会</span></li>\n<li class=\"col-lg-2\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">親睦会</span></li>\n<li class=\"col-lg-2\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">提案制度</span></li>\n<li class=\"col-lg-3\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">社内ベンチャー制度</span></li>\n<li class=\"col-lg-5\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">イノベーション創造チャレンジ</span></li>\n<li class=\"col-lg-5\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">補助金(サークル活動）</span></li>\n<li class=\"col-lg-5\"><span class=\"welfare-item\">各種試験支援、お祝金制度</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"recruit-page-bg recruit-page-bg--white mt-0 pt-0 pb-0\" id=\"recruit-work-circle\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<h2 class=\"recruit-protrusion-heading\">サークル活動</h2>\n<ul class=\"row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 gx-2 gy-4 list-unstyled mb-0\">\n<li class=\"col\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"border-radius-20 d-block mx-auto\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-7.jpg\" srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-7@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"recruit-place-circle-caption\">ＩＣＳ野球部</span></li>\n<li class=\"col\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"border-radius-20 d-block mx-auto\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-8.jpg\" srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-8@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"recruit-place-circle-caption\">ＩＣＳフットサルクラブ</span></li>\n<li class=\"col\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"border-radius-20 d-block mx-auto\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/place/img-recruit-work-place-9.jpg\" srcset=\